---
title: Smoky Bone-In Pork Chops with Roasted Vegetables and Chimichurri Aioli
description: Our chimichurri aioli's creamy texture and herbaceous flavour makes it the star of this Argentinian take on the classic pork chop dinner. You'll dollop it over juicy pork chops seasoned with our Smoked-Paprika Garlic Spice Blend, plus use it as a dip for potatoes coins, blistered tomatoes and a roasted pepper and onion medley.
